Create a Constant

Source: R/op-constant.R
hlo_constant.Rd

Create either a scalar or tensor constant.

Usage

hlo_scalar(value, elt_type = NULL, ...)

# S3 method for class 'logical'
hlo_scalar(value, elt_type = NULL, ...)

hlo_tensor(value, elt_type = NULL, ...)

Arguments

value

(any)
Value from which to create a constant.

elt_type

(character(1))
String for element type. Can be one of f64, f32, u8, u16, u32, u64, i8, i16, i32, i64, pred.

...

(any)
Additional arguments.
